{"tid":2098760,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"確診者曾訪一田百貨沙田分店 沙田店今日停業消毒","createTime":"2020-07-07T17:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T17:45:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ea8a3f48d8966bd5295ea62ce90700946b04730c","tid":2098760,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T17:23:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/121200.\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F121200.&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=2c7a046a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/121200.</a><br />\n<br />\n確診者曾訪一田百貨沙田分店 沙田店今日停業消毒<br />\n<br />\n沙田一田百貨表示，接獲通知指有新型肺炎確診患者曾經到訪沙田分店，因此沙田店今日停業一日。一田百貨說，已安排專業人士為全店深度清潔及消毒，以保障顧客及同事安全，沙田店將於明日重開。<br />\n<br />\n2020-07-08 01:16:29"},{"pid":"32857ba7c7db72a52f32f520b76c1e7226d51af7","tid":2098760,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea8a3f48d8966bd5295ea62ce90700946b04730c","tid":2098760,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T17:23:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/121200.\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F121200.&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=2c7a046a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/121200.</a><br />\n<br />\n確診者曾訪一田百貨沙田分店 沙田店今日停業消毒<br />\n<br />\n沙田一田百貨表示，接獲通知指有新型肺炎確診患者曾經到訪沙田分店，因此沙田店今日停業一日。一田百貨說，已安排專業人士為全店深度清潔及消毒，以保障顧客及同事安全，沙田店將於明日重開。<br />\n<br />\n2020-07-08 01:16:29"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T17:27:13.000Z","msg":"永續武肺"},{"pid":"29085fe98bf441e129081b54b0a97ab55303ec28","tid":2098760,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T17:27:32.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" c